   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="writingSession" n="1"><opener><seg type="letterhead"><seg rend="left"><pb facs="MS-B-00005-B-000-00063"/><hi rend="pre-print">»<rs ref="#pmb29209" type="org">Die Zeit</rs>«</hi></seg><seg rend="right"><hi rend="pre-print"><hi rend="bold"><rs ref="#pmb50" type="place">Wien</rs></hi>, den</hi><space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><date>24. <hi rend="latintype">September</hi><space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><hi rend="pre-print">189</hi>6</date></seg></seg><seg type="letterhead"><seg rend="left"><hi rend="pre-print">Wiener Wochen<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>chrift</hi></seg><seg rend="right"><hi rend="pre-print"><rs ref="#pmb296" type="place">IX/3, Güntherga<c rendition="#langesS">s</c><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>e 1</rs>.</hi></seg></seg><seg type="letterhead"><hi rend="pre-print"><hi rend="bold">Herausgeber</hi>:</hi><lb/><hi rend="pre-print">Profe<c rendition="#langesS">s</c><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>or Dr. <rs ref="#pmb12790" type="person">I. Singer</rs>, <rs ref="#pmb10815" type="person">Hermann Bahr</rs>,
                        Dr. <rs ref="#pmb11867" type="person">Heinrich Kanner</rs>.</hi></seg><seg type="letterhead"><hi rend="pre-print">Telephon Nr. 6415.</hi></seg><salute rend="center">Lieber Arthur!</salute></opener><p>Be<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>ten Dank für Deine liebe Gratulation – an dem <anchor type="commentary" xml:id="K_L00598-1"/><rs type="work" ref="#pmb30461" subtype="implied">Stück</rs><note type="commentary" corresp="K_L00598-1">Am 
                   <date>22. 9. 1896</date> fand die <rs type="event" subtype="implied" ref="#pmb35403">Uraufführung</rs> von <rs ref="#pmb30461" type="work">Juana</rs> am <rs ref="#pmb45434" type="org">Berliner Neuen Theater</rs> statt.</note> i<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>t ja nichts, ich habe nur einmal probieren wollen, ob man mit dem bloßen
               Ver<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>tande ein »gutes <rs type="work" ref="#pmb30461" subtype="implied">Theater<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>tück</rs>«<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>chreiben kann, und es<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>cheint fa<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>t, daß mir das für <rs ref="#pmb168" type="place">Berlin</rs> gelungen i<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>t.</p><closer>Herzlich<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>t<lb/>Dein<lb/><signed>Hermann</signed></closer><p><hi rend="pre-print"><anchor type="textConst" xml:id="T_L00598-1"/>Alle für »<rs ref="#pmb29209" type="org">Die Zeit</rs>« be<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>timmten Zu<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>chriften und Sendungen<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>ind an die
                  Redaction der »<rs ref="#pmb29209" type="org">Zeit</rs>« und <hi rend="bold">nicht</hi> an die Per<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>on eines der Herausgeber zu richten.<note type="textConst" corresp="T_L00598-1">am unteren Rand der Seite</note></hi></p></div>
      </body>
